---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';

const article = { author: "Maine Dispensary Guide Editorial Team", publishDate: "2026-01-20", modifiedDate: "2026-03-21", section: "Operations & Technology" };
---

<Layout 
  title="POS Systems for Maine Dispensaries | Maine Dispensary Guide" 
  description="In-depth technical resource for POS Systems for Maine Dispensaries within the Maine cannabis industry. Professional 2026 guidance on licensing, compliance, and strategic market positioning."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742044-3c52d6e88c62?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
  article={article}
>
  <article>
    <div class="article-header">
      <h1>POS Systems for Dispensaries</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Choosing the right point-of-sale system for your Maine cannabis dispensary</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Why Cannabis-Specific POS Matters</h2>
      <p>General retail POS systems won't work for cannabis dispensaries. You need specialized software that handles <a href="/glossary/#seed-to-sale">seed-to-sale</a> tracking, compliance reporting, and cannabis-specific regulations.</p>
    </section>

    <Callout title="The Engine of Your Shop" type="tip">
      Your <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-pos/">POS system</a> is the central nervous system of your dispensary. Choosing a system that feels intuitive and exciting to use will empower your team to provide the best possible experience for your customers. It's where your community's needs meet your business's efficiency.
    </Callout>

    <section>
      <h2>Key Features Required</h2>
...
        <li>Ensure Maine compliance before choosing</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="further-reading">
      <h2>Further Reading</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Office of Cannabis Policy (OCP)</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use/tracking" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Seed-to-Sale Tracking Info</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="disclaimer">
      <p><em>Pricing and features are subject to change. Verify current information with providers.</em></p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  article { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .article-header { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
  section { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  section h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  section h3 { margin-top: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1rem 0; }
  th, td { padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  th { background: var(--color-background); }
  ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .disclaimer { background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffc107; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; }
  .further-reading { background: rgba(88, 129, 87, 0.05); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  .further-reading h2 { margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.25rem; }
</style>
